  "text": "The target is assumed, for simplicity, to be rotationally symmetric (many targets of interest are, such as land mines and UXO [CITATION_1] , [CITATION_2] , [CITATION_3] ) and, therefore, the top two terms along the diagonal are degenerate (these correspond to the two directions perpendicular to the target axis of rotation).",
